{"tid":2442713,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：愛黨是中共黨員的責任 但我並非中共黨員","createTime":"2021-03-11T13:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T01:18:45.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"be63468852570d68e2b260d5fe70565272f1f083","tid":2442713,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"對於候選人是否需要「愛中國共產黨」？林鄭指這非新制度的要求，但應尊重中共是中國的執政機關。<span class=\"red\">她又指，愛黨是中共黨人的責任，自己並非中共黨員</span>，但要接受香港是中國一部份，而根據《憲法》第一條，中共是中國大陸的執政機關。<br />\n<br />\n對於外國的反應，她指已有心理準備，外國政府會粗暴干預中國內部事務。又指只要港府拘捕涉嫌違反《國安法》、被歐美認為是民主派的人士，便會批評港府，甚至要求放人，林鄭不點名質疑有關人士是否知道甚麼是「法治」。林鄭相信，今次對方亦會指控香港民主倒退。<span class=\"red\">至於制裁方面，林鄭強調不會嚇怕他們，雖然家人會受影響，但願意「捨小家為大家」</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/VG4GZVVWSJEFDBFZDKPW7IEHZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FVG4GZVVWSJEFDBFZDKPW7IEHZ4%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=12948c88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FVG4GZVVWSJEFDBFZDKPW7IEHZ4%2F&h=b29a0830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/VG4GZVVWSJEFDBFZDKPW7IEHZ4/</a>"},{"pid":"c6f1b16df51f4fd7242834805df20f2719e0603d","tid":2442713,"uid":93600,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"你係地下黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecdd0ac69c8d668a00465b675f312aaee0a0eb1","tid":2442713,"uid":189715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"嘩"},{"pid":"465843e9d2c9eccc30b42c92114ece6bc5d3cbd5","tid":2442713,"uid":18477,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">咁即係由你嘅自由意志決定奶共啦</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30efbdd5b9a9bd9eff1e3deb6b37